    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible, showroom-quality shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I've babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away and spotless. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection inside and out. I'm really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely fall in love with it. Come take a look and see for yourself; you won't be disappointed!",
