    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "An exceptional specimen of the E46 M3, this vehicle features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, utilizing high-pressure VANOS variable valve timing and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. This chassis has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring structural integrity and longevity. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with zero bushing deflection. The exterior retains its original luster with all VIN tags present, while the cabin shows no bolster wear or pixel degradation. A mechanically synchronized, investment-grade example of BMW\u2019s finest engineering.",
